00:46:15.362 --> 00:46:17.304
But that's how sin would be forgiven.

00:46:20.248 --> 00:46:22.411
And therefore the will of God cannot be undone.

00:46:22.451 --> 00:46:25.855
It will be fulfilled in perfection.

00:46:25.915 --> 00:46:34.305
Paul and the saints here in Glenburne.

00:46:36.688 --> 00:46:41.554
An apostle sent one of Jesus Christ by the will of God.

00:46:42.466 --> 00:46:50.319
to the saints who are in Glen Bernie and faithful in Christ Jesus.

00:46:50.819 --> 00:46:56.529
Grace to you and peace from God our Father and the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:46:57.250 --> 00:47:04.882
Blessed be the God and Father of our Lord Jesus Christ who has blessed us with every spiritual blessing in heavenly places

00:47:04.962 --> 00:47:15.136
in Christ, just as He chose us in Him before the foundation of the world that we should be holy and without blame before Him in love.

00:47:15.637 --> 00:47:16.098
Thank you.

00:47:16.138 --> 00:47:16.819
We bless you.

00:47:16.859 --> 00:47:19.803
We praise you for making us holy and without blame.

00:47:19.843 --> 00:47:24.369
Lord, I pray a blessing upon your people today, a special warmth of your love.

00:47:24.490 --> 00:47:30.418
And Lord, I pray as we enter into just a couple days before Christmas and all that comes with it,

00:47:30.530 --> 00:47:40.579
that we can rest in you, rest our heart, our head against the bosom of God and hear the word spoken to us of how your heart beats for us.

00:47:41.140 --> 00:47:52.250
Thank you for giving us just a moment to slow down before this Christmas and to sit at your feet and to rest and hear your heart beat for us.

00:47:52.891 --> 00:47:53.412
We love you.

00:47:53.672 --> 00:47:55.233
In your name, amen.

00:47:56.154 --> 00:47:56.474
Amen.

00:47:56.514 --> 00:47:57.235
God bless you.

00:47:57.315 --> 00:48:00.338
Christmas Eve, if you can make it, if not,

00:48:00.482 --> 00:48:04.914
Read the newspaper next week we'll be talking some amazing things.
